                        <h3 class="border-b pb-1 mb-3">Heads Up Display (HUD)</h3>

                        <p>
                            The text and visual components that appear in front of the 3D view.
                        </p>

                        <div class="c-well my-3">
                            <div class="row my-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <div class="text-center">
